    "Additional details about the calculation of the F 1 score are discussed in the Supplementary Discussion.",
    "We found that the performance of the models is contingent on the property being extracted.",
    "Both LLMs exhibit superior performance relative to the NER-based MaterialsBERT pipeline in extracting data for bandgap, while accuracy declines when extracting data for Tg (Fig. 3f, g).",
    "GPT-3.5 achieved the highest F 1 score of 0.67 for Tg, with the Similar-shot selection method slightly outperforming the Random selection method.",
    "Materi-alsBERT and LlaMa obtained F 1 scores of 0.63 and 0.64, respectively."
